-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

snippet.title: New Mahindra XEV 9e & BE 6e First Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Mahindra just unveiled their two new electric-origin SUVs, XEV 9e and BE 6e. Both are based on their new INGLO platform and feature the most extensive battery pack and most powerful electric motors of an Indian-made electric Car. The indicative price of BE 6e is Rs 18.90 lakh Ex Showroom for base trim while as, the XEV 9e on the other hand cost Rs 21.90 lakh for base trim Ex-Showroom.  Here is an in-depth video of both XEV 9e and BE 6e. 

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
00:38 Mahindra BE 6e Exterior walkaround, including Key Fob, Wheels, Headlights, Tail, Boot Space, Front Trunk etc
09:20 Interiors of Mahindra BE 6e including Screens, Steering, Features, Sunroof, Seats, Space, HUD etc
25:40 Rear seat space and amenities on Mahindra BE 6e.
27:41 Mahindra XEV 9e Exterior walkaround, including Key Fob, Wheels, Headlights, Boot Space, Front Trunk
32:15 Interiors of Mahindra XEV 9e SUV including Screens, Steering, Features, Sunroof, Seats, Space, HUD etc
37:30 Rear seat space and amenities of XEV 9e
41:28 Conclusion

snippet.title: Victory Anthem | Khushi TDT | Lashcurry | Audiocrackerr | Official Lyrical Video
snippet.description:
Thankyou for the crazy response on Victory Anthem!¬†Watch the official lyric video of this banger now and comment your favourite line!

#victoryanthem #khushitdt #lashcurry 

Credits:
Written & performed by- Khushi & Lashcurry
Prod.by - Audiocrackerr
Mix & Mastered by - Xolo

Lyrics:
Hook
Badi Baatcheet Industry Ke Logo Se
Poori Picture Bachi Abhi Promo Dekh
Mere Kisse Sunoge Toh Ro Doge 
Lashcurry Khushi Bakchodi Ni Dono Se
Bhali Bhaati Hume Roka Bhuto Ne 
Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Kea 
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

Khushi's Verse 
Rukegi Kalam Ni Jab Tak Hu Zinda Main
Marungi Tab Tak Ni Kala Hai Zindaa
Mujhe Lagta Hai Jaanti Sab Hu Main
Haar Ya Jeet Ki Hoti Ni Chinta..
Main Sunti Hu Logo Ko Jyada Ni
Par Haa Main Jaanti Sabke Hu Dil Ka
Mere Hote Padosi Ameer Jo Paisa Yaha 
Baatein Banane Se Milta..

Lo Aadat Daal Main Ruku Ye Hoga Ni
Socha Ni Kisi Ni Karungi Sab...
Paiso Se Laakho Ka Bharungi Pet Mein
Mujhe Ni Kamanaa Bharne Ko Ghar 
Phele Bhi Bola Hai Maqsad Ni Hai Mera 
Kamana Paisa Ya Kamana Fame
Faraq Hai Mujhe Badalni Hai Duniya 
Aur Tumhe Badalne Hai Ghar

Karne Se Baatein Hojati Hai Taaza
Wo Yaadein Ki Kaise Kara Maine Shuru Tha Tab
Koi Ni Tha Mere Sath Mein Rone Ko
Aaiyne Mein Baitha Guru Tha Bass
Kehte The Log Tere Baski Ni Tha Mera 
Dil Bhi Naadan Tha Maanta Sach
Par Kuch Ni Hai Aisa Jo Tu Ni Karskti 
Ab Kehta Hai Aaiyna Kehte Hai Sab

Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Ke
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

Lashcurry Verse
Sangeet Ko Sab Kiya Samarpit
Likhe Dill Se Gaane Hai Mere Ameer Geet
Bigie Paak Ko Sun Gaya Safar Beet 
Meri Baate Hai Raw No More Color Grid

Meri Maa Se Puchhna Mere Baare Me 
Baap Se Ladi Vo Bete Ko Gaane De
Saath Me Khadi Me Uske Sahare Se 
To Kese Socha Tune Ki Hum Haarenge 

Kitni Dafa Me Gira Kitni Dafa Me Utha 
Kitna Dafa Khuda Me Mujhko Dua Me Suna
Kabhi Ni Ruka Jhuka Ni Kabhi Ni Muda Vuda Me
Kabhi Ni Kisi Ke Baare Kabhi Ni Bola Bura Me 

Damn Mere Aakho Pe Patti Baandh 
Mujhe Dekhna Ni Hate Karu Haq Ki Baat 
Hum Dono Banane Chale Hai Legacy 
Ek Beat Pe Khushi Aur Lashcurry Saath

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Let the new games begin.

Squid Game Season 2 arrives December 26.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys¬Æ becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 283 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

New players. New rules. After each round, every player gets to vote "O" to stay or "X" to leave ‚Äî and a changed Gi-hun is determined to shake up the game.

snippet.title: Ding Liren vs Gukesh | Game 3 | FIDE World Championship Match 2024 | Ft. Sagar, Tania and Samay
snippet.description:
Watch it LIVE in person in Habitat in Mumbai: https://in.bookmyshow.com/sports/world-chess-championship-broadcast-2024-gukesh-v-ding-liren/ET00420952

The FIDE World Championship 2024 match is the first in 138 years to feature two contestants from Asia, the reigning World Champion, China‚Äôs Ding Liren and challenger Dommaraju Gukesh from India competing for the title and a prize fund of US$2.5 million.

The schedule of the World Championship match takes place over 3 weeks, with 14 match days and 4 rest days planned. All games start at 17:00 local time (2.30 p.m. IST) and there are rest days after Games 3, 6, 9 and 12. The first player to reach 7.5 points will be the winner; in the case of a tie after 14 games, tiebreaks will be played the next day to decide the winner.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Man City 3-3 Feyenoord | Haaland (2), Gundogan, Hadj-Moussa, Gimenez, Hancko Goals
snippet.description:
City manager Pep Guardiola said the manner of a dramatic 3-3 Champions League draw at home to Feyenoord was ‚Äòa difficult one to swallow‚Äô.

Manchester City lost a three-goal advantage as we were held to a 3-3 draw by Feyenoord in the Champions League.

Erling Haaland struck twice, his first making him the fastest player to 50 goal involvements in Champions League history when he scored from the penalty spot just before the break in just his 44th appearance in the competition.

They came either side of Ilkay Gundogan‚Äôs volley for his first goal back at the Etihad Stadium since returning in the summer.

But the Dutch side scored three times in the final 15 minutes through Anis Hadj Moussa, Santiago Gimenez and David Hancko to grab a point.

snippet.description:
"This song is a reimagined version of the classic Bollywood track 'Dhiktana Dhiktana', transformed into a melancholic reflection on loneliness and disillusionment. By flipping the upbeat original into a somber tone, the song conveys the harsh reality that no one in this world truly belongs to you. It redefines the familiar melody to evoke a sense of sadness and introspection, making it a poignant commentary on isolation and unfulfilled connections.

snippet.title: IPL 2025 Mega Auction Tamil| Updated Squad List of teams Day 2 |CSK MI RCB RR DC PBKS KKR SRH LSG GT
snippet.description:
IPL 2025 Mega Auction Tamil| Updated Squad List of teams Day 2|CSK MI RCB RR DC PBKS KKR SRH LSG GT

#ipl #ipl2025 #iplauction

IPL 2025 Auction Day 1: Franchises spend Rs 467.95 Cr for 72 players, Rishabh Pant most expensive
ndian players stole the show with Rishabh Pant, Shreyas Iyer and Venkatesh Iyer bagging the most money on Day 1.
IPL 2025 auction Day 1: Out of 577 players on the short list, only 72 players were sold. However, out of Rs 641. 5 Cr, teams already spent Rs 467.95 Cr on Day 1, leaving just Rs 173.55 Crore on the table for 132 players on Day 2. On Day 1, Indians were the top picks. Lucknow Super Giants broke the bank, splashing Rs 27 Crore for Rishabh Pant. Minutes before that, Punjab Kings bagged Shreyas Iyer for Rs 26.75 Cr. Kolkata Knight Riders made Venkatesh Iyer the third most expensive player at Rs 23.75 Cr.
Punjab Kings who came to the auction with Rs 110.5 Cr spent the most. They splashed 88.0 Cr for 10 players. Royal Challengers Bengaluru are left with the most purse on Day 2 with 30.65 Cr. Sunrisers Hyderabad will be a mute spectator on Day 2 as they are left with just Rs 5.15 Cr.

snippet.title: Pennine ishtayo? | 4k | Short film | full movie | Sajin | Gopika anil | Achu sugandh
snippet.description:
Pennine Ishtayo - A Musical Short Film | Official Release
"Pennine Ishtayo" is a captivating Malayalam musical short film that explores the deep emotions of love, human connection, and the power of music. Directed by Achu Sugandh and produced by Nithin Thaivalappil under Filmika Cinemas, this film features powerful performances by Sajin Shiva, Gopika Anil, and an ensemble cast of talented actors. With stunning visuals by Rejin Santo and soul-stirring music composed by Bonny Louis, this film is sure to resonate with viewers of all ages.

From the mesmerizing vocals by Sadhika K R, Neethusha A C, Arjun, Nithin K Shiva, and Bonny Louis, to the skillful dance choreography by Surya R K, Pennine Ishtayi is a complete sensory experience that beautifully blends narrative and music.

Key Credits:

Written & Directed by: Achu Sugandh
Produced by: Nithin Thaivalappil, Filmika Cinemas
Cinematography (DoP): Rejin Santo

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.description:
Are you ready for the most exhilarating day in cricket? The IPL 2025 Mega Auction has arrived, and this video brings you all the highlights from Day 1! Discover which players were snapped up by all 10 teams and witness the intense bidding battles that kept fans on the edge of their seats. 

Join us as we break down the full list of sold players, analyze key team strategies, and discuss surprising moves that could change the game this season. Whether you're a die-hard fan or new to IPL, this insider‚Äôs look at one of cricket's biggest events will keep you informed and excited for what's next. Don‚Äôt miss out‚Äîhit play now!

________________________________________

Cricket is a bat-and-ball game played between two teams of eleven players. A 22-yard (20-meter) pitch has a wicket at each end, two bails balanced on three stumps. The batting side scores runs by striking the ball bowled at the wicket with the bat (and running between the wickets). In contrast, the bowling and fielding side tries to prevent this (by preventing the ball from leaving the field and getting the ball to either wicket) and dismiss each batter (so they are "out"). Means of dismissal include bowling when the ball hits the stumps and dislodges the bails. The innings ended when ten batters were dismissed, and the teams swapped roles. The game is adjudicated by two umpires, aided by a third umpire and match referee in international matches.

Forms of cricket range from Twenty20, with each team batting for a single inning of 20 overs, to Test matches played over five days. Traditionally, cricketers play in an all-white kit but wear club or team colors in limited-overs cricket. In addition to the basic kit, some players wear protective gear to prevent injury caused by the ball. A complex, solid spheroid made of compressed leather with a slightly raised sewn seam enclosing a cork core layered tightly wound string.

Dil-e-Nadan Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Mikaal Zulfiqar - Amar Khan - Ali Abbas - 26th November 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Nayab is a simple girl who, after losing her parents, lives with her grandmother and brother. Her sister-in-law takes advantage of her simplicity, burdening her with all household chores and stunting her personal growth.

Zaviyaar, a successful man from a wealthy family, is paired with Nayab by his grandmother due
to her naivety and simplicity. After rebelling against his family and rejecting his cousin Tania to marry Nayab, Zaviyaar soon becomes frustrated with her lack of education and grooming. Hurt by Zaviyaar‚Äôs rejection, Tania increases the rift between Nayab and Zaviyaar, causing tension and conflict in their marriage.

Will Zaviyaar and Nayab‚Äôs marriage withstand the schemes of Tania? Can Nayab change herself for Zaviyaar? Will she find support from Zaviyaar‚Äôs family, or will she face everything alone? Will Zaviyaar regret marrying Nayab? Will Tania be able to separate Zaviyaar and Nayab?

Nayab is a simple girl who, after losing her parents, lives with her grandmother and brother. Her sister-in-law takes advantage of her simplicity, burdening her with all household chores and stunting her personal growth.

Zaviyaar, a successful man from a wealthy family, is paired with Nayab by his grandmother due
to her naivety and simplicity. After rebelling against his family and rejecting his cousin Tania to marry Nayab, Zaviyaar soon becomes frustrated with her lack of education and grooming. Hurt by Zaviyaar‚Äôs rejection, Tania increases the rift between Nayab and Zaviyaar, causing tension and conflict in their marriage.

Will Zaviyaar and Nayab‚Äôs marriage withstand the schemes of Tania? Can Nayab change herself for Zaviyaar? Will she find support from Zaviyaar‚Äôs family, or will she face everything alone? Will Zaviyaar regret marrying Nayab? Will Tania be able to separate Zaviyaar and Nayab?

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
